propActionIcon:
An IconButton element to be used as secondary action target
(primary action target is the item itself).
propClasses: Override or extend the styles applied to the component.
propSubtitle: String or element serving as subtitle (support text).
stylesRoot: Styles applied to the root element.
stylesPositionBottom: Styles applied to the root element if `position="bottom"`.
stylesPositionTop: Styles applied to the root element if `position="top"`.
stylesPositionBelow: Styles applied to the root element if `position="below"`.
stylesTitleWrap: Styles applied to the title and subtitle container element.
stylesTitleWrapBelow: Styles applied to the title and subtitle container element if `position="below"`.
stylesTitleWrapActionPosLeft: Styles applied to the container element if `actionPosition="left"`.
stylesTitleWrapActionPosRight: Styles applied to the container element if `actionPosition="right"`.
stylesTitle: Styles applied to the title container element.
stylesSubtitle: Styles applied to the subtitle container element.
stylesActionIcon: Styles applied to the actionIcon if supplied.
stylesActionIconActionPosLeft: Styles applied to the actionIcon if `actionPosition="left"`.
